{{Infobox company | name = Ascom Group| logo = | type = [[Joint stock]] | slogan = | foundation = 1994| location = [[Chişinău]]| key_people = [[Anatol Stati]], CEO| num_employees = 500| revenue = US$ 500 million (2007)| industry = [[Oil]] and [[natural gas]]| products = [[Oil|Oil products]], [[natural gas]]| homepage = [http://www.ascom.md/ Official site] }}
''' Ascom Group ''' is the largest [[oil]] and [[gas]] company in [[Moldova]]. The company has commercial operations in [[Kazakhstan]], [[Turkmenistan]] and [[Sudan]] and produces around 500,000 tonnes of [[oil]] and around 1.3 billion m<sup>3</sup> of [[natural gas]] per year.
The company owns in [[Kazakhstan]] proven reserves of 13 million tonnes of [[oil]] and 10 billion m<sup>3</sup> of [[natural gas]].<ref>[http://www.interlic.md/Economie/3221.html Ascom-Grup a realizat investitii de 600 mil. USD in sectorul petrol si de gaze al Kazahstanului {{ro}}] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919041642/http://www.interlic.md/Economie/3221.html |date=September 19, 2008 }}</ref>
