The '''Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Bloemfontein''' ({{lang-la|Bloemfonteinen(sis)}}) is the [[Metropolitan bishop|Metropolitan]] [[Episcopal See|See]] for the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Bloemfontein]] in [[South Africa]].
==History== * 1951.01.11: Established as Metropolitan Archdiocese of Bloemfontein from the [[Apostolic Vicariate of Aliwal]] and the [[Apostolic Vicariate of Kimberley]] in South Africa.
==Special churches== The seat of the archbishop is [[Sacred Heart Cathedral, Bloemfontein]].
